{"id":691651,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/691651.html","date":"2023-01-04T02:18:37Z","modified":"2023-01-04T06:05:05Z","title":"卖杏花｜我只希望没有在这个国家遇到你","content":"<div style=\"width:42%;float:right;padding-left:20px\">\n<div class=\"su-spoiler su-spoiler-style-fancy su-spoiler-icon-chevron-circle su-spoiler-closed\" data-scroll-offset=\"0\" data-anchor-in-url=\"no\"><div class=\"su-spoiler-title\" tabindex=\"0\" role=\"button\"><span class=\"su-spoiler-icon\"></span>CDT 档案卡</div><div class=\"su-spoiler-content su-u-clearfix su-u-trim\"><br />\n<strong>标题：</strong>我只希望没有在这个国家遇到你<br />\n<strong>作者：</strong>孙旭阳<br />\n<strong>来源：</strong><a href=\"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s/wnVDKAGe-LDnfhuFIE_k_g\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">微信公众号“卖杏花”</a><br />\n<strong>发表日期：</strong>2023.1.2<br />\n<strong>主题归类：</strong><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/tag/新冠疫情\" target=\"_blank\">新冠疫情</a><br><br />\n<strong>CDS收藏：</strong><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/space/%E5%85%AC%E6%B0%91%E9%A6%86\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">公民馆</a><br><br />\n<strong>版权说明：</strong>该作品版权归原作者所有。中国数字时代仅对原作进行存档，以对抗中国的网络审查。<a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/copyright\">详细版权说明</a>。<br />\n</div></div>\n</div>\n<p>跨年那夜</p>\n<p>我躺在老家殡仪馆门口</p>\n<p>办手续的亲人在办手续</p>\n<p>我把座椅放平</p>\n<p>想恢复一点精力</p>\n<p>却不停咳</p>\n<p>爬出车外</p>\n<p>我打量天上的半月</p>\n<p>空气中</p>\n<p>有雾霾</p>\n<p>也有焚尸炉涌出的粉尘</p>\n<p>我的鼻腔和肺叶告诉我</p>\n<p>它比煤灰细</p>\n<p>比草木灰沉</p>\n<p>都快十一点了</p>\n<p>殡仪馆大院里人来人往</p>\n<p>吹手铜器</p>\n<p>呜呜啦啦</p>\n<p>那些死于“感冒”的老人</p>\n<p>一定不愿意看到子孙和路人</p>\n<p>在今晚</p>\n<p>会因他们而咳</p>\n<p>有老人去咳</p>\n<p>去死</p>\n<p>就已经够了</p>\n<p>我很后悔在这个国家</p>\n<p>认识这些老人</p>\n<p>我更希望</p>\n<p>没有在这个国家遇到你</p>\n<p>我们的爱与护持</p>\n<p>不应该是分享一板布洛芬</p>\n","author":1067,"categories":[45870,41492,43134,45438,45443],"tags":[46339,43499,45262,45298,45432]}